@startuml

actor Organization
participant "RefugeeLink App" as App
participant "Formation Student List" as List
participant Database

Organization -> App: Log in
Organization -> App: Navigate to formation
App -> Database: Retrieve student list for formation
Database --> App: Student list
Organization -> App: Toggle approval status of student
App -> Database: Update student approval status
Database --> App: Confirmation of update
App --> Organization: Confirmation message

@enduml
